Class Completables

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.akarnokd.rxjava2.operators.Completables

  • public final class Completables
extends java.lang.Object
    Additional operators in the form of CompletableConverters, use Completable.as(CompletableConverter) to apply the operators to an existing sequence.

    0.20.2
